isty in St. Petersburg, Fla., on April 26, 2026.</media:text><media:description type="plain">Nahida Bristy.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260427-nahida-bristy-mn-0755-97059b.jpg" height="402" width="602"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 15:43:38 GMT</pubDate><title>Remains of missing University of South Florida student confirmed through DNA</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 15:50:19 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 11:25:56 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The Justice Department released chilling new surveillance video of the man charged with trying to assassinate President Donald Trump at the White House Correspondents’ Dinner. Prosecutors say it shows Cole Allen casing the Washington Hilton the day before the attack. New evidence photos also show bags of ammunition inside his room as well as a gas mask and protective glasses. NBC’s Gabe Gutierrez reports for TODAY.</description><expires>2056-05-01T11:25:06.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501</guid><link>https://www.today.com/video/doj-releases-new-video-of-assassination-suspect-casing-hotel-262516293652</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>DOJ Releases New Video of Assassination Suspect &#39;Casing&#39; Hotel</media:title><media:player url="https://www.today.com/video/doj-releases-new-video-of-assassination-suspect-casing-hotel-262516293652"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777634697864_tdy_news_7a_gutierrez_whcd_shooter_videos_260501_S3_1920x1080-428tqn.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">The Justice Department released chilling new survei